A Northern group, known as Arewa Northern Action Front, has called on the North to join the ‘RevolutionNow’ protest since, according to the group, President Muhammadu Buhari has continued working with a cabal of Mamman Daura, Ismaila Funtua and Abba Kyari. The Arewa group said that the northern Nigeria has been pushed to the wall […] Northern group finally joins RevolutionNow protest, gives reasons Source: Daily Post